definitions.definition: The armpit , or the cavity beneath the junction of the arm and shoulder .
The area that is located posterior to the transscutal articulation and anterior to the scutoscutellar suture .

main_definition: The armpit , or the cavity beneath the junction of the arm and shoulder .
secondary_definitions: ( entomology ) The area that is located posterior to the transscutal articulation and anterior to the scutoscutellar suture .
( botany , uncommon ) Alternative form of axil .
